OL,3,C'Gentlest soul' taxi driver one of
OL,4,Cfour killed in head-on collision
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox reports from the scene
OL,9,FA taxi driver killed in a head-on
OL,10,Fcollision has been described as the
OL,11,F"gentlest soul" by his family, as
OL,12,Fpolice name those who died.
OL,14,FUber driver Mosrab Ali, 54, was one of
OL,15,Ffour who died at the scene in Bolton,
OL,16,Ffollowing the crash between his
OL,17,FCitroen C4 Picasso and a red Seat
OL,18,FLeon, in the early hours of Sunday 11
OL,19,FJanuary.
