OL,3,C'Gentlest soul' taxi driver one of
OL,4,Cfour killed in head-on collision
OL,6,FThree teenagers in the other car were
OL,7,Falso killed and have been named as
OL,8,FMohammed Jibrael Mukhtar, 18, Farhan
OL,9,FPatel, 18 and Muhammad Danyaal, 19.
OL,11,FTwo women and three men are currently
OL,12,Fin hospital following the collision.
OL,14,FMr Ali's family said he had worked as
OL,15,Fa taxi driver for around 10 years and
OL,16,Fdescribed him as the "gentlest soul".
OL,18,FHis oldest child, Humayra, 29, said:
OL,19,F"Nobody has a bad word to say against
OL,20,Fhim, he was so kind and the best dad.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
