OL,3,C'Gentlest soul' taxi driver one of
OL,4,Cfour killed in head-on collision
OL,6,F"When they knocked on our door and
OL,7,Ftold us what had happened I was just
OL,8,Fso confused.
OL,10,F"Dad was such a safe driver and even
OL,11,Fwhen we said we were worried something
OL,12,Fmight happen he would say 'don't worry
OL,13,Fabout me'."
OL,15,FMosrab's family say they were told he
OL,16,Fwas killed instantly in the collision
OL,17,Fand would not have suffered any pain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
