OL,6,F"The police have been wonderful,"
OL,7,FHumayra added. "They said the mortuary
OL,8,Fis normally closed at weekends but
OL,9,Fthey arranged for it to be opened so
OL,10,Fwe could go and see dad and say
OL,11,Fgoodbye."
OL,13,FThe collision happened just before 1am
OL,14,Fas the taxi drove along Wigan Road and
OL,15,Fis being investigated by Greater
OL,16,FManchester Police (GMP).
OL,18,FFive passengers from both vehicles
OL,19,Fremain in hospital for treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
