OL,6,FIn the Citroen, a 29-year-old woman
OL,7,Fsuffered potentially life-threatening
OL,8,Finjuries, a 28-year-old woman and a 30-
OL,9,Fyear-old man suffered serious injuries
OL,10,Fand a 29-year-old man has minor
OL,11,Finjuries, the force said.
OL,13,FAn 18-year-old man, who was a
OL,14,Fpassenger in the Seat, remains in
OL,15,Fhospital for treatment of minor
OL,16,Finjuries.
