OL,6,FDetective Inspector Andrew Page, of
OL,7,Four Serious Collision Investigation
OL,8,FUnit, said: "We are still in the early
OL,9,Fstages of our investigation and work
OL,10,Fis ongoing to establish the full
OL,11,Fcircumstances of this terrible
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,F"As an investigation team we would
OL,15,Fencourage people to be mindful of
OL,16,Fsharing footage on social media given
OL,17,Fthe impact this will have on all the
OL,18,Ffamilies involved in such a tragic
OL,19,Fincident.
