OL,6,F"Thanks to patrols in the area, teams
OL,7,Fwere able to get to the incident
OL,8,Flocation quickly to what was a
OL,9,Fparticularly challenging scene for
OL,10,Fcolleagues in the emergency services.
OL,12,F"I want to thank first responders from
OL,13,Four Bolton district and the Road
OL,14,FPolicing Unit, alongside colleagues
OL,15,Ffrom Greater Manchester Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service and the North West
OL,17,FAmbulance Service for their hard work
OL,18,Fsince this incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
