OL,6,F"The scene closed on Sunday evening,
OL,7,Fbut we are still appealing for any
OL,8,Fwitnesses to come forward. Anyone who
OL,9,Fsaw the vehicle driving before the
OL,10,Fcollision, witnessed the incident
OL,11,Fitself, or has dashcam/ CCTV footage
OL,12,Fof the incident can share it with us."
